        <p>With the given distance, <italic>d</italic>, a expansion vector, <inline-formula><mml:math id="M25"><mml:mover class="overrightarrow"><mml:mrow><mml:mi>E</mml:mi></mml:mrow><mml:mo>â</mml:mo></mml:mover></mml:math></inline-formula>, would then be generated using by the following expressions:</p>
